snippet.title: Big Tower Tiny Square 2 Reveal
snippet.description:
Big Square has rebuilt the original Big Tower with traps and mechanics from the previous Towers! 

A mix of familiar and frustration awaits as you make your way up the Big Tower 2 - the 5th instalment of the Big Tower Tiny Square series!
